<text xml:lang="ta">
  <body>
    <div xml:id="Aink77-kilavi">
      <p type="edition">muṉṉoru ñāṉṟu talaiviyōṭu puṉalāṭiṉāṉ eṉak kēṭṭu ivaṉuṭaṉ iṉi āṭēṉeṉa uṭkoṇṭa parattai, ‘putup puṉal āṭap pōtu’ eṉṟa talaimakaṟkuc colliyatu.
      </p>
      <p type="translation" xml:lang="en"> </p>
    </div>
    <div xml:id="Aink77">
      <lg type="edition">
<l>amma vāḻiyō makiḻnaniṉ moḻival</l>
<l>pērū ralareḻa nīralaik kalaṅki</l>
<l>niṉṉoṭu taṇpuṉa lāṭutu</l>
<l>memmoṭu ceṉmō cellaṉiṉ maṉaiyē.</l>
</lg>

<lg type="translation" xml:lang="en">


<l> Ah me, long life to you, o delightful man! </l> 
<l> I have something to tell you: </l> 
<l> We shall bathe with you in the cool flood </l> 
<l> until gossip rises up in the big village</l> 
<l> as ripples are stirred up on the water.  </l> 
<l> Come with us! Do not go [back] to your house. </l> 



</lg>
    </div>
